<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-the-other-hand">on the other hand</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>(可是) 另一方面：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On the one hand, computers improve the working efficiency; on the other hand, they also bring about some new problems.
一方面，计算机提高了人们的工作效率，另一方面，也引起了一些新的问题。</p></div></div>